  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12\" data-layout-label=\"Post Body\" data-type=\"item\" id=\"item-6874c6136a2003590e8bd12a\"><div class=\"row sqs-row\"><div class=\"col sqs-col-12 span-12\"><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"e1d7fe477a068834fe2c\" id=\"block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h3 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>大器優雅、沈穩中帶有設計細節<br></strong>兼具實用性與美感的 Mikado Quartz 帝雉石，打造理想居家空間</h3><p class=\"\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"></p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-e1d7fe477a068834fe2c .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block image-block sqs-block-image\" data-block-type=\"5\" data-sqsp-block=\"image-classic\" id=\"block-cf374ac1304080bbdb1b\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n    \n  \n    <div\n        class=\"\n          image-block-outer-wrapper\n          layout-caption-below\n          design-layout-inline\n          combination-animation-none\n          individual-animation-none\n          individual-text-animation-none\n        \"\n        data-test=\"image-block-inline-outer-wrapper\"\n        data-sqsp-image-classic-block-layout=\"inline\"\n    >\n\n      \n\n      \n        <figure\n            class=\"\n              sqs-block-image-figure\n              intrinsic\n            \"\n            style=\"max-width:800px;\"\n        >\n          \n        \n        \n\n        \n          \n            \n          <div\n              \n              \n              class=\"image-block-wrapper\"\n              data-animation-role=\"image\"\n              \n  \n\n          >\n            <div data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image-container class=\"sqs-image-shape-container-element\n              \n          \n        \n              \n            \" style=\"\n                position: relative;\n                \n                  padding-bottom:56.25%;\n                \n                overflow: hidden;-webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(white, black);\n              \"\n              >\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n                <img data-stretch=\"false\" data-src=\"/images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg\" data-image=\"/images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg\" data-image-dimensions=\"800x450\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"\" data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" data-sqsp-image-classic-block-image src=\"/images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw\" style=\"display:block;object-fit: cover; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-position: 50% 50%\" onload=\"this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)\" srcset=\"/images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 100w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 300w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 500w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 750w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 1000w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 1500w, /images/1752483347078-7NLMJ6LJ55A4MKVTW0ZP/_.jpeg 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        \n          \n        \n\n        \n      \n        </figure>\n      \n\n    </div>\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"157e2c4026c2b80b8b17\" id=\"block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><pre><code>大器優雅、沈穩中帶有設計細節，是 Arthur 張嘉予律師居家空間帶來的第一個視覺感受，那麼帶來更加療癒心靈的觸覺呢？「回到家一腳踩下玄關地板，一種難以言喻的踏實感襲來，這是沒有體驗過的人無法想像的感覺。」Arthur 在風格獨具的家中，別出心裁地挑選帶有內斂紋理的 Black Jasper 黑色帝雉石作為地板材料，首先為雙腳提供了撫慰與歸屬感。 誠摯地分享親身感受的 Arthur 表示：「如果我沒有踩過，也不會相信有什麼差別。」而抗污不吃色、耐磨高硬度的特質，都是帝雉石材十分適合作為玄關地板空間的原因，對於的Arthur接著補充道，也彷彿為帝雉石作爲地板材質的運用做了絕佳的示範。</code></pre><p class=\"\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"></p><h4 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>帝雉石藝術品般的吸引力</strong></h4><pre><code>Arthur的居家空間由琢隱設計操刀規劃，整體以他偏好的深色為主基調，完美混搭木質、石材與少量的金屬材質，副凡變化性的同時，亦不失整體性。其中，帝雉石在 Arthur 家中扮演了多重且與眾不同的重要角色：運用於空間裡總計 9 處的大、小平面，4 種花紋各異的帝雉石從最為常見的廚房檯面，到玄關地板、檯面與牆面、主客浴洗手檯面與淋浴間置物櫃，還有以白色Polar Land花紋組成的沙發背牆，大面積的形式成為空間中的視覺焦點之一，也成為設計主軸。「我很喜歡藝術品，我覺得好的石材就像藝術品一樣，Polar Land 彷彿是雪地的感覺，潑墨般的效果是我非常喜愛的元素，也如同抽象畫，上頭無論掛畫與否，都是家中風格很好的展示。」 過去曾經歷家中廚房檯面裂開的經驗，Arthur 對於廚房檯面的材質選擇以實用性為首要考量，抗熱、耐刮又不吃色的特性，讓 Arthur 毫無懸念地選擇淺灰色素面帝雉石來擔綱此大任。然而因帝雉石獨特又豐富的花紋圖騰，因此一改帝雉石原本僅要使用於廚房檯面的計畫，將之材延伸至家中其他處，Polar Land 的款式更是成為家中的一大看點，甚至也產生家中地板全改以帝雉石材的念頭。</code></pre></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-157e2c4026c2b80b8b17 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-spacer spacer-block sized vsize-1\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.spacer/523604b1-74b7-4792-97e8-b24d3d8ea8c8_1064/website.components.spacer.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.spacer/523604b1-74b7-4792-97e8-b24d3d8ea8c8_1064/website.components.spacer.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.spacer\" data-website-component-id=\"0c58f220d1ad79f5601d\" id=\"block-0c58f220d1ad79f5601d\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">&nbsp;</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"71a2acee36fa616750b1\" id=\"block-71a2acee36fa616750b1\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h4 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">天然大理石的實用性落差</h4><pre><code>選用特殊色天然大理石作為中島，Arthur 坦言儘管色彩與花紋美麗，使用時仍較為不自在。「在廚房做菜時，我甚至會在帝雉石檯面切食材，但是在天然大理石的中島時我真的會有所顧慮，後來也不太在中島做菜了。」喜愛於家中煎牛排、喝紅酒的他，從不擔心帝雉石油煙清潔與吃色的問題，可看出對於帝雉石材的放心程度與天然大理石材難以比較。「儘管後來中島多用於暫放提袋與東西，然而若是包袋上有金屬小配件，也會擔心是否碰傷大理石。」，Arthur 接著說道：「如果有朋友想以石材作為中島設計的材料，除非真的非常特殊的花紋與色彩，否則我覺得都應該使用帝雉石，因為相同的視覺效果，實用性差太多了。」 日本工業設計大師深澤直人曾言「讓人沒有感覺的設計才是好設計」，正是因為能夠乘著直覺，順暢、無顧慮地使用，才能夠讓使用者「無感」，也似乎是帝雉石的使用註解。完整了 Arthur 個人的理想居家，帝雉石無論在視覺、觸覺上，皆能自然地與居家生活細節互動，創造最為放鬆的體驗！</code></pre></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-71a2acee36fa616750b1 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-spacer spacer-bl